title House of Hummus

participant Main
participant FoodTruck
participant Entrees
participant API
participant Vegetables
participant Sides
participant Sales
participant OrderButton
participant TransientState
    
Main->>FoodTruck: renderAllHTML()
FoodTruck->>Entrees: entree options
Entrees->>API: fetch /entrees
API-->>Entrees: return [entrees] array
Entrees-->FoodTruck: return radio buttons
 
FoodTruck->>Vegetables: vegetable options
Vegetables-->API: fetch /vegetables
API->>Vegetables: return [vegetables] array
Vegetables-->FoodTruck: return radio buttons

FoodTruck->>Sides: side options
Sides-->API: fetch /sides
API->>Sides: return [sides] array
Sides-->>FoodTruck: return radio buttons

FoodTruck->>Sales: sales list
Sales-->API: fetch /purchases
API->>Sales: return [purchases] array
Sales-->FoodTruck: return receipt
    
Main->>TransientState: setting functions setEntree(id), setVegetable(id), setSide(id), isOrderComplete()
 
Main<--TransientState: TRUE! 
Main->>TransientState: if true, getOrder()
TransientState-->OrderButton: Return the selected current order
OrderButton->>TransientState: Click! Here is the selected order for permanent data

  
Sales->>OrderButton: take this receipt number for the order
TransientState-->API: POST to permanent data and save it
Main->>FoodTruck: Generate HTML strings for the main container
    
Main<--TransientState: clearOrder(), ready for new selections
FoodTruck<<-Main: Ready for next order! Re-render!